- VSCode Version: 1.3.0
- OS Version: win8 64bit

Steps to Reproduce: open vs code, file -> preferences -> keyboard shorcuts
enter:

// Place your key bindings in this file to overwrite the defaults
[
  {
    "key": "ctrl+e",
    "command": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "ctrl+e ctrl+d",
    "command": ["eslint.fixAllProblems", "editor.action.format"]
  }
]

i think the problem is the array commands, after entering this vs code cannot be used any more
need to open the json shortcuts file from %appdata% and edit it manualy
